# 🛡️ User Registration System

[![Build](https://img.shields.io/badge/build-passing-brightgreen.svg)](https://github.com/manisha123M/userregistration/actions)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Made with React](https://img.shields.io/badge/Frontend-React-blue)](https://reactjs.org)
[![Made with Express](https://img.shields.io/badge/Backend-Express.js-green)](https://expressjs.com)
[![PostgreSQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/Database-PostgreSQL-336791.svg?logo=postgresql)](https://www.postgresql.org/)

A full-stack user registration and login system using **React**, **Node.js (Express)**, and **PostgreSQL**. Focused on secure authentication and data protection.

----

## 🚀 Tech Stack

| Frontend | Backend           | Database   |
| -------- | ----------------- | ---------- |
| React    | Node.js + Express | PostgreSQL |

---

## ✨ Features

* 🔐 Encrypted email storage
* 🔏 Password validation on registration
* 📄 Forms:
  * Register: name, section, email, password, address
  * Login: email, password
* 🧭 Dashboard with placeholder buttons (UI in progress)
* 🎨 Custom CSS styling (no HTML files used)

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

### 📁 Clone the Repository

```
git clone https://github.com/manisha123M/userregistration.git
cd userregistration
```

---

### 🛠️ Backend Setup

1. Navigate to backend directory:

   ```
   cd backend
   ```

2. Install dependencies:

   ```
   npm install
   ```

3. Create a `.env` file:

   ```
   DB_USER=your_pg_username
   DB_PASSWORD=your_pg_password
   DB_NAME=your_database_name
   DB_HOST=localhost
   DB_PORT=5432
   ```

4. Start the server:

   ```
   npm start
   ```

---

### 🎨 Frontend Setup

1. Navigate to frontend directory:

   ```
   cd ../frontend
   ```

2. Install dependencies:

   ```
   npm install
   ```

3. Start the frontend:

   ```
   npm start
   ```

Visit:
🔗 `http://localhost:3000` — React frontend
🔗 `http://localhost:5000` — Express backend

---

